{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/responsive-web-design-v9/workshop-final-exams-table/step-4","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"workshop-final-exams-table","demoType":null,"title":"Korak 4","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Element zaglavlja tabele se sastoji od elementa <dfn>red u tabeli</dfn>, <code>tr</code>, koji sadrži elemente <dfn>zaglavlje ćelije tabele</dfn>, <code>th</code>.</p>\n<p>Evo primera korišćenjem elemenata <code>tr</code> i <code>th</code> za sportsku tabelu:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-html\">&#x3C;table>\n  &#x3C;caption>Football Scores&#x3C;/caption>\n  &#x3C;thead>\n    &#x3C;tr>\n      &#x3C;th>Team&#x3C;/th>\n      &#x3C;th>Wins&#x3C;/th>\n      &#x3C;th>Losses&#x3C;/th>\n    &#x3C;/tr>\n  &#x3C;/thead>\n&#x3C;/table>\n</code></pre>\n<p>Unutar vašeg <code>thead</code> elementa, dodajte element <code>tr</code>.</p>\n<p>Unutar vašeg <code>tr</code> elementa, dodajte tri <code>th</code> elementa.</p>\n<p>Prvi <code>th</code> element mora sadržati tekst <code>Last Name</code>. Drugi <code>th</code> element mora sadržati tekst <code>First Name</code>. Treći <code>th</code> element mora sadržati tekst <code>Grade</code>.</p>\n</section>","id":"66a9bcf00f13a418368a272e","hasEditableBoundaries":true,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":0,"helpCategory":"HTML-CSS","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"responsive-web-design-v9","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":null,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/responsive-web-design-v9/workshop-final-exams-table/step-4"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":true,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"indexhtml","ext":"html","name":"index","contents":"<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n  <head>\n    <title>Calculus Final Exams Table</title>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\" />\n  </head>\n  <body>\n    <table>\n      <caption>\n        Calculus Final Exam Grades\n      </caption>\n\n      <thead>     \n        \n      </thead>\n    </table>\n  </body>\n</html>","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[13,15],"history":["index.html"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p>Trebalo bi da imate otvarajući tag <code>tr</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.match(code, /<tr>/i);"},{"text":"<p>Trebalo bi da imate zatvarajući tag <code>tr</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.match(code, /<\\/tr>/i);"},{"text":"<p>Vaš <code>tr</code> element treba da bude unutar vašeg <code>thead</code> elementa.</p>","testString":"const trEl = document.querySelector('tr');\nassert.strictEqual(trEl?.parentElement?.tagName, 'THEAD');"},{"text":"<p>Vaš prvi <code>th</code> element bi trebalo da ima tekst od <code>Last Name</code>.</p>","testString":"const thEl = document.querySelectorAll('th')[0];\nassert.strictEqual(thEl?.textContent.trim(), 'Last Name');"},{"text":"<p>Vaš drugi <code>th</code> element treba da ima tekst od <code>First Name</code>.</p>","testString":"const thEl = document.querySelectorAll('th')[1];\nassert.strictEqual(thEl?.textContent.trim(), 'First Name');"},{"text":"<p>Vaš treći <code>th</code> element bi trebalo da ima tekst od <code>Grade</code>.</p>","testString":"const thEl = document.querySelectorAll('th')[2];\nassert.strictEqual(thEl?.textContent.trim(), 'Grade');"},{"text":"<p>Svi vaši elementi <code>th</code> bi trebalo da budu unutar vašeg elementa <code>tr</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.match(code, /<tr>.*<th>.*<\\/th>.*<th>.*<\\/th>.*<th>.*<\\/th>.*<\\/tr>/is);"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/responsive-web-design-v9/#workshop-final-exams-table","dashedName":"step-4","certification":"responsive-web-design-v9","disableLoopProtectTests":false,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"responsive-web-design-v9","chapter":"html","module":"html-forms-and-tables","block":"workshop-final-exams-table","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/responsive-web-des